OL,3,CAsda beats big-name tea brands to be
OL,4,Cnamed nation's 'best cuppa'
OL,6,FAsda has beaten big-name brands such
OL,7,Fas PG Tips, Tetley and Twinings in a
OL,8,Ftaste test to find Britain's best cup
OL,9,Fof tea.
OL,11,FAsda's Everyday Tea Bags achieved the
OL,12,Ftop score of 72% in a blind tasting by
OL,13,F79 "experienced and committed" tea
OL,14,Fdrinkers assembled by consumer group
OL,15,FWhich?.
OL,17,FThe tasters commended the product,
OL,18,Fcosting #1.20 for 80 bags, for its
OL,19,Faroma and appearance, with 68% judging
OL,20,Fthe colour as perfect and 49% finding
OL,21,Fthe flavour to be "just right".
