OL,3,CAsda beats big-name tea brands to be
OL,4,Cnamed nation's 'best cuppa'
OL,6,FTied at the bottom of the table on 67%
OL,7,Fwere Twinings Everyday and Tesco
OL,8,FOriginal Tea.
OL,10,FAt #4.80 per 80 bags, Twinings cost
OL,11,Ffour times the price of Asda's winning
OL,12,Foffering, and while more than 60% of
OL,13,Ftasters liked the colour and
OL,14,Fbitterness level of Twinings, fewer
OL,15,Fthan half were satisfied with the
OL,16,Fstrength of flavour.
OL,18,FWhile two thirds of the panel enjoyed
OL,19,Fthe bitterness of Tesco Original, 35%
OL,20,Fsaid it was too dark and 34%
OL,21,Fconsidered it not to be strong enough.
