OL,3,CAsda beats big-name tea brands to be
OL,4,Cnamed nation's 'best cuppa'
OL,6,FNatalie Hitchins, Which? head of home
OL,7,Fproducts and services, said: "A cup of
OL,8,Ftea is a daily essential for millions
OL,9,Fand many of us will passionately
OL,10,Fdefend our favourite brand.
OL,12,F"Our results show that the bigger and
OL,13,Fmore expensive brands aren't
OL,14,Fnecessarily the best for taste, with a
OL,15,Fsupermarket own-brand costing less
OL,16,Fthan 2p per cup emerging ahead of
OL,17,Frivals costing up to four times as
OL,18,Fmuch.
